Simple Modal version 0.1

Sample Code

HTML

<div id="YourName"></div>

$("#yourName").modal({ style: 'error'});


Options for Simple Modal



Style: (string) 
You have three options.  

You can load an Error, Message or HTML page.  This option is required for the Modal to run.

style: 'error',
style: 'message',
style: 'html'

text: (string)
If you use the style Error or Message this is the text to fill the Modal


url: (string)
If you use the style HTML this is the URL you would like to present;


cancel: (callback)
Callback for when the close Button is hit


reportError: ( boolean)
Visibility of Report Error Button in the modal

reportURL:  (string)
URL of hyperlink for Report Error Button

